**Download the lastest package from the website

tar xvzf eclipse*.tar.gz -C /tmp/


**Relocation
sudo su -c "chown -R root:root /tmp/eclipse && mv /tmp/eclipse /opt/eclipse-mars"


**Making Symlink

sudo su -c "ln -s /opt/eclipse-luna/eclipse /usr/local/bin/eclipse-luna"

**Bug Fix for closing when launching 
export SWT_GTK3=0

**Old version remove
sudo apt-get autoremove eclipse*
rm -r ~/.eclipse/